{"tid":1211034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地撤退啦！","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:48:04.000Z","uid":154012,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fcdb445dc26c11465cd25378697ad56038b63f","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"講真，其實今日要做嘅目的都達到左，就係要佢取消會議<br />\n點解仲唔走<br />\n對方已經換過批人，隨時做足準備<br />\n而家嘅我地根本打唔過，夜晚比佢地捉左去角落做啲咩未必有人會留意到<br />\n呢場仗可能要打好耐，不如返屋企好好咁抖下<br />\n留返啲力再搏殺啦<br />\n我知，最終嘅目的係要佢撤銷條例 <br />\n但係 你而家去搏盡咁之後仲有邊個會肯出嚟呢<br />\n求下你地，我唔想見到再有人受傷<br />\n今日我都係度，望住啲犬一個一個催淚彈扔過嚟，<br />\n點解可以咁埋沒自己嘅良心，大家都係人，<br />\n見到啲市民比啲犬射傷打傷，甚至比人拉左<br />\n真係好心up，班犬根本已經無得救，無曬良心<br />\n點解香港會變成咁<br />\n返去抖一抖，儲足精力再去搏過<br />\n既然今日可以成功做到，代表將來都可以！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油！香港人！<br />\n你地今日已經做得好好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未來香港需要你地！"},{"pid":"c21970217a990c97cd003d188d95a05553c1d1e9","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"好心up呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1229f17bb868c5c78babb3f104dbb44f1220377","tid":1211034,"uid":240355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a39f12049bf847b44543ec334aa42c6eecca24","tid":1211034,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"走啊"},{"pid":"4d747da39fa7324fb16f1ddcac05facaf68031cf","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"點解白車都可以唔比入，唔比去救人<br />\n我地都係人，個個都有血有肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14000827e2c6f2c428507c7e7d7ee4e142d53b89","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"佢地而家根本做足準備，咩裝備都齊曬<br />\n一行動，我地個個都有機會受傷<br />\n甚至比人拉返去做埋啲陰濕行動<br />\n唔想見到你地咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583362feb339dfff86ebb6f80fd5abc08efd43d2","tid":1211034,"uid":234704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"唔好再有義士受傷pls，越夜班狗越顛架！！"},{"pid":"cadf0fc013c20d8eefbcb51339bcdb3c9ae2822d","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"583362feb339dfff86ebb6f80fd5abc08efd43d2","tid":1211034,"uid":234704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"唔好再有義士受傷pls，越夜班狗越顛架！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"真係，夜晚鏡頭未必影得清楚佢地做過啲乜"},{"pid":"4cff9935d868ff1511ab8baeb57fc7948059298b","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"今日可能令到佢地取消，其實已經做得好好！"},{"pid":"85f541034db7294d4b814e37c46668bbfd33c1cc","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cff9935d868ff1511ab8baeb57fc7948059298b","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"今日可能令到佢地取消，其實已經做得好好！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"*可以"},{"pid":"e457a9847e6696c1324a3bfa990c8c4005f2b133","tid":1211034,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:03:05.000Z","msg":"走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20030d15f0f8aba4ad3ed952823978e3dc3cfc60","tid":1211034,"uid":207867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc0a62278522bbd8b76dff23a0e5b06473e8b49","tid":1211034,"uid":89549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:04:43.0